<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.212446>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Leptobrachium xanthops sp. nov. in life. (A) Lateral view, (B) eye with palpebrum retracted, (C) dorsal view, and (D) ventral view of the male holotype NCSM 78468. (E) Lateral view and (F) ventral view of the female paratype NCSM 78467. The upper iris and scleral arc are pale yellow in life, but appear near to white under camera flash." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/212446/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

